<item>
            <title>[LU-11611] Incorrect return value in mdt_reint_unlink</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-11611</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Added by recent landing of &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/31425&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/31425&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-comment&quot;&gt;/* We will lock the child regardless it is local or remote. No harm. */&lt;/span&gt;
        mc = mdt_object_find(info-&amp;gt;mti_env, info-&amp;gt;mti_mdt, child_fid);
        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (IS_ERR(mc))
                GOTO(unlock_parent, rc = PTR_ERR(mc));

        &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (!cos_incompat) {
                rc = mdt_object_striped(info, mc);
                &lt;span class=&quot;code-keyword&quot;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (rc &amp;lt; 0)
                        GOTO(unlock_parent, rc = PTR_ERR(mc));
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;this last PTR_ERR should clearly be just &quot;rc&quot;. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
